ZH: 资本是创业的基础。
EN: Capital is the foundation of entrepreneurship.

ZH: 这个项目需要大量的资本支持。
EN: This project requires extensive capital support.

ZH: 对于企业来说，融资是获取资本的重要途径之一。
EN: For businesses, fundraising is one of the important ways to acquire capital.

ZH: 成功的创业者通常具备一定的资本积累。
EN: Successful entrepreneurs usually have a certain amount of capital accumulation.

ZH: 创业需要勇气和足够的资本。
EN: Entrepreneurship requires courage and sufficient capital.

ZH: 资本运作可以极大地推动经济发展。
EN: Capital operation can greatly promote economic development.

ZH: 投资是一种有效的资本运作方式。
EN: Investment is an effective way of capital operation.

ZH: 创业者要善于利用现有的资本资源。
EN: Entrepreneurs need to be good at utilizing existing capital resources.

ZH: 资本市场的波动会影响企业的发展方向。
EN: Fluctuations in the capital market can affect the direction of company development.

ZH: 企业家需要具备良好的资本运作意识。
EN: Entrepreneurs need to have a good awareness of capital operation.

ZH: 资本的流动可以加快资源配置的速度。
EN: The flow of capital can accelerate the speed of resource allocation.

ZH: 这家企业依靠自己的资本实力迅速崛起。
EN: This company quickly rose to prominence through its own capital strength.

ZH: 资本投资可以带动区域经济的发展。
EN: Capital investment can drive regional economic development.

ZH: 公司的资本结构对其经营活动具有重要影响。
EN: The capital structure of a company has a significant impact on its operational activities.

ZH: 资本运作需要一定的风险意识和判断力。
EN: Capital operation requires a certain risk awareness and judgment.

ZH: 对于创新型企业来说，资本是推动创新的重要支撑。
EN: For innovative enterprises, capital is an important driver of innovation.

ZH: 这个行业需要大量的资本投入才能发展。
EN: This industry requires a large amount of capital investment to develop.

ZH: 资本市场的繁荣有助于提升经济整体水平。
EN: The prosperity of the capital market contributes to the overall improvement of the economy.

ZH: 资本的流通使得资源能够得到更好的利用。
EN: The circulation of capital enables resources to be utilized more effectively.

ZH: 这家公司依靠资本市场的支持实现了快速发展。
EN: This company achieved rapid development with the support of the capital market.
